---
title: Homestyle Beef & Bacon Filo Pie with Avocado Salad
description: Imagine a savoury filling of tender beef and crispy bacon, seasoned to perfection and topped with layers of flaky, golden filo pastry. Each bite is a delightful crunch followed by a burst of hearty goodness. Perfect for a cozy dinner or a crowd-pleasing party dish, this pie is a flavour-packed treat that will have everyone asking for seconds.
